---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Over Pagayo" description="Leer hoe Pagayo ondernemers helpt om direct te starten en op te schalen." lang="nl">
	<Header />
	<main class="about-page">
		<section class="hero">
			<p class="eyebrow">Over Pagayo</p>
			<h1>Gebouwd voor ondernemers die meteen willen beginnen</h1>
			<p class="lead">Binnen 30 seconden je eigen omgeving live, zonder gesprekken of installaties. Alles wat je nodig hebt om te verkopen zit er al in.</p>
			<div class="hero-actions">
				<a class="btn primary" href="https://beheer.pagayo.com">Start gratis</a>
				<a class="btn ghost" href="/nl/contact">Heb je vragen? Neem contact op</a>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="pillars">
			<div class="pillar">
				<h3>Direct live</h3>
				<p>Account aanmaken, wachtwoord kiezen en je webshop staat klaar met je eigen link.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="pillar">
				<h3>EÃ©n platform</h3>
				<p>Webshop, abonnementen, kassa en verhuur in dezelfde omgeving. Geen losse systemen.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="pillar">
				<h3>Groei zonder gedoe</h3>
				<p>Betaal minder procent naarmate je meer omzet draait en schaal door zonder limieten.</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="story">
			<h2>Waarom we Pagayo bouwden</h2>
			<p>Ondernemers verloren tijd aan gesprekken, implementaties en losse tools. Daarom hebben we een platform gemaakt dat direct werkt: je klikt op Start gratis en je hebt binnen een halve minuut je eigen omgeving. Geen wachttijd, geen onboardingkosten.</p>
		</section>

		<section class="stats">
			<div class="stat">
				<span class="stat-number">30s</span>
				<span class="stat-label">van signup naar live</span>
			</div>
			<div class="stat">
				<span class="stat-number">5000+</span>
				<span class="stat-label">omgevingen actief</span>
			</div>
			<div class="stat">
				<span class="stat-number">99,98%</span>
				<span class="stat-label">beschikbaarheid</span>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="cta">
			<h2>Klaar om te starten?</h2>
			<p>Maak je account aan en krijg direct de link naar je eigen webshop. Geen demo of call nodig.</p>
			<div class="cta-actions">
				<a class="btn primary" href="https://beheer.pagayo.com">Start gratis</a>
				<a class="btn ghost" href="/nl/contact">Hulp nodig? Neem contact op</a>
			</div>
		</section>
	<style>
		.about-page { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 120px 1.75rem 90px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 3rem; }
		.eyebrow { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.4rem; padding: 0.35rem 0.9rem; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 999px; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.85rem; }
		.hero { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0,255,136,0.12), rgba(0,0,0,0.9)); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 18px; padding: 2.5rem; box-shadow: 0 14px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.35); }
		.hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2.3rem, 4vw, 3.4rem); margin: 0; line-height: 1.15; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
		.lead { color: var(--text-secondary); max-width: 760px; line-height: 1.6; }
		.hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 0.8rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
		.btn { text-decoration: none; padding: 0.85rem 1.4rem; border-radius: 10px; font-weight: 700; border: 1px solid var(--border); display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 0.45rem; }
		.btn.primary { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent) 0%, #00e077 100%); color: #06130d; }
		.btn.ghost { color: var(--text); }
		.pillars { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem; }
		.pillar { border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 14px; padding: 1.4rem; background: var(--bg-secondary); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.18); }
		.story { border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 14px; padding: 1.6rem; background: var(--bg-secondary); }
		.story h2, .cta h2 { margin-bottom: 0.6rem; }
		.stats { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem; }
		.stat { border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.3rem; background: rgba(0,255,136,0.05); text-align: center; }
		.stat-number { display: block; font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent); }
		.stat-label { color: var(--text-secondary); }
		.cta { border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; padding: 1.8rem; background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0,255,136,0.08), rgba(0,0,0,0.9)); text-align: center; box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.25); display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.8rem; }
		.cta-actions { display: flex; gap: 0.8rem; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; }
		@media (max-width: 768px) { .hero { padding: 2rem; } }
	</style>
	<Footer />
</BaseLayout>
